{
  "texts": [
    "The articles retrieved in WOS and Scopus can be further refined into social science or educational categories, allowing for more precise retrieval.",
    "Additionally, given the focus of this research on the use of technology in education, the IEEE database provides focused research in scientific and technical disciplines.",
    "Two stages comprise the processes used to identify the research papers.",
    "In the first stage, the keyword \"SR\" was selected, and the discipline was refined to \"education and educational research\".",
    "This process yielded 309 articles."
  ]
}